":141060,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"三叔高階機買完送藍牙耳機"},{"pid":"b967356b394bd81aa957a02b76e2cd1ac87ffd34","tid":2168284,"uid":127251,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"傳 Samsung 反其道而行 &nbsp; 重新為旗艦提供 3.5mm 耳機插孔<br />\n<br />\nApple 在 iPhone 取消 3.5mm 耳機插孔後，不少用戶都改為使用藍牙耳機，亦造就後來的 AirPods 成為熱賣商品。很多 Android 手機廠商亦陸續取消 3.5mm 耳機插孔，改為以 USB-C 接口連接耳機，這個安排並非所有用戶都滿意，有消息指 Samsung 正打算撥亂反正。<br />\n<br />\n著名爆料人 @MauriQHD 早前在 Twitter 透露，Samsung 正在考慮在 2021 至 2022 年間，重新為 Galaxy S 和 Galaxy Note 系列配備 3.5mm 耳機插孔，不過這個構想還在討論階段，就算實行亦可能屬於試驗性質，只會為期一年。相信 Samsung 希望藉此試探用戶和市場的反應，看看有多少 Android 廠商會跟隨。<br />\n<br />\n現時市場上仍然提供 3.5mm 耳機插孔的中高階手機不多，Sony 和 LG 是其中兩間，但其他主流品牌的中高階手機，大多數都已經取消了 3.5mm 耳機插孔。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：cnbeta<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/216424/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F216424%2F1%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9586afec\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/216424/1/</a>"},{"pid":"25bcfc8a26cba31837bfd1c8692bc86b54ff5ab3","tid":2168284,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ba055895c0d924e578cd0268e353d569936d7fd","tid":2168284,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"s10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d341fb04018950a72cc9c2f5a1336ed92e8ba37d","tid":2168284,"uid":25971,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"daf8fa3c3bff6a4308e656012fa6e003397706f1","tid":2168284,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係。。。lightning/TypeC 轉3.5mm會比直接內置3.5mm輸出得高啲呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T00:55:47.000Z","msg":"理論上個3.5插係底板上會有干擾，用type c/lightning 轉插係冇咁多雜訊<br />\n但實際上手機聽又可以好聲得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d318c9665daf3a33625d588e3934907f07e062c","tid":2168284,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"隔離罪大都加翻啦，係Samsung自己唔加姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}